[div class=p 
	"In this game you choose two characters and control them both simultaneously. 
	$LF
	"Use D-pad to move the first person, press "A" to stop ghosts with your proton beam, then press "B" in appropriate moments to catch them by the second ghostbuster. Unfortunately, he has incredibly stupid AI, and it's hard to make him move in desired direction. Often it's not so easy to determine in which order do you have to catch ghosts (if you are planning to save time, of course).
	$LF
]div
